
'Pillow' is a web framework that maps URIs to Pillow pages ([efanXtra]`afEfanXtra` components), letting them react to RESTful events.

'Pillow'...
 - Is a [BedSheet]`afBedSheet` framework
 - Extends [efanXtra]`afEfanXtra` components
 - Plays great with [Slim]`afSlim`
 - Runs on [IoC]`afIoc`

'Pillow' - Something for your web app to get its teeth into!
